headline: Citi Raises Autodesk (ADSK) Price Target, Maintains Buy Rating
summary: On Tuesday, May 27, Citi analyst Tyler Radke increased the price target on Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK) from $374 to $376 and kept a “Buy” rating. This adjustment came after the company reported financial results for Q1 of fiscal 2026. According to Radke, the results were solid and showed a good balance of growth and margin […]
